node.text:
@williemoorejrlive was adopted at 3 months and never met anyone in his biological family. 
. 
He has now release a new documentary called “The Missing Peace Movie” to share his story and inspire other foster youth.
.
Visit @williemoorejrlive bio to purchase the tickets to watch his documentary and story.

node.title: @williemoorejrlive is a Radio host, speaker & best selling author
